Preparations for <setup.py>:
from distutils.core import setup                                     
setup(                                                               
    name = 'findStr',                                                
    version = '1.0.0',                                               
    py_modules = ['findStr'],                                        
    author = 'kavon ma',                                             
    author_email = 'kavon.ma@alcatel-lucent.com',                    
    url = 'https://github.com/kavonm',                               
    description = 'find a specified string in a file',               
    data_files = [('lib/python3.2/site-packages', ['data/data.txt'])]
)                                                                    

Action 1: initial setup
1. python setup.py sdist
2. python setup.py install
3. python setup.py sdist upload

Action 2: update
1. modify version in setup.py
2. python setup.py sdist upload
